    "2-categories, this layered structure can be depicted as in figure 2.Given that layering structure of genuine and non-genuine operators is so similar to the layering structure inherent in the mathematics of higher-categories, one might then wonder whether genuine and non-genuine higher-charges can be combined into the structure of a higher-category."
